  "description": "This dataset contains raw neuroimaging data from a study investigating real-time, personalized brain state-dependent transcranial magnetic stimulation (TMS) in healthy adults. The research demonstrates that personalized whole-brain activity patterns can predict human corticospinal tract activation in real-time, enabling adaptive brain stimulation protocols tailored to individual neural signatures.",
  "methods_description": "Real-time and offline analysis of brain activity patterns to predict corticospinal tract activation, with personalized TMS delivery based on individual whole-brain activity signatures.",
